text: Abdul Khaleque Molla is an Indian politician belonging to All India Trinamool Congress. He was elected as MLA of Metiaburuz Vidhan Sabha Constituency in West Bengal Legislative Assembly in 2016.List of Winners in West Bengal 2016 ==References== Category:Living people Category:All India Trinamool Congress politicians Category:West Bengal MLAs 2016– Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
